00:33:03,565 --> 00:33:06,648
'Now, starfighters,
if you will reach underneath your seats,

326
00:33:06,776 --> 00:33:10,394
'you will find a packet
which contains one...'

327
00:33:14,034 --> 00:33:16,992
this is a restricted area,
off-limits to...

