My apologies, starfighter.

329
00:33:22,792 --> 00:33:26,125
Star navigator first class grig
at your service, sir!

330
00:33:28,924 --> 00:33:31,006
Hi. I'm Alex rogan.

331
00:33:31,134 --> 00:33:33,574
I was playing this game back home,
and this guy came up to me.

332
00:33:33,678 --> 00:33:35,634
Only he's not a guy, he's an alien, right?

333
00:33:35,764 --> 00:33:38,301
And I get into his car,
only it's not a car, it's a spaceship.

334
00:33:38,433 --> 00:33:41,641
And, uh... there's been a big mistake.

335
00:33:41,770 --> 00:33:45,979
Am I to understand you're actually declining
the honor of becoming a starfighter?

336
00:33:46,107 --> 00:33:49,190
- You got it.
- Extraordinary!

337
00:33:49,861 --> 00:33:54,070
For eons, all creatures have dreamt
of being starfighters.

338
00:33:54,199 --> 00:33:56,190
- Where are you from?
- Earth.

339
00:33:56,326 --> 00:33:59,443
And we're not at war with anybody
except each other.

340
00:33:59,579 --> 00:34:03,288
Earth? Earth isn't a formal member
of the star league,

341
00:34:03,416 --> 00:34:05,702
