the Excalibur test.

351
00:34:34,781 --> 00:34:36,396
It was called a video game.

352
00:34:36,533 --> 00:34:40,947
What's all the brouhaha?
After all, he does have the gift.

353
00:34:41,079 --> 00:34:43,365
This may come as a bit
of a shock to you,

354
00:34:43,498 --> 00:34:45,830
but he doesn't want to be a starfighter.

355
00:34:46,585 --> 00:34:49,668
