He could be the greatest starfighter ever!

363
00:35:12,777 --> 00:35:15,484
- That was a game, centauri.
- A game?

364
00:35:16,906 --> 00:35:19,693
You may have thought it was a game,
but it was also a test.

365
00:35:19,826 --> 00:35:21,441
A-ha! A test!

366
00:35:21,578 --> 00:35:26,038
Sent out across the universe to find
those with the gift to be starfighters.

367
00:35:26,166 --> 00:35:29,203
And here you are, my boy.
Here you are!

368
00:35:29,336 --> 00:35:32,794
- Right! Here I am, about to be killed!
- Killed...

369
00:35:33,882 --> 00:35:37,124
You don't seriously think
it's dangerous, do you?

370
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:39,797
Don't be silly. Trust me.

371
00:35:57,947 --> 00:35:59,312
Xur!

372
00:35:59,908 --> 00:36:01,239
Xur!

373
00:36:01,868 --> 00:36:03,108
Xur?

374
00:36:04,996 --> 00:36:10,741
Yes, father, your mighty frontier
grows weaker by the moment.

375
00:36:10,877 --> 00:36:14,085
Do not call me father!

376
00:36:14,798 --> 00:36:17,164
You are no longer my son!

377
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:20,588
