put down your xurian cult.

382
00:36:34,734 --> 00:36:37,441
Your followers are few and scattered.

383
00:36:37,570 --> 00:36:39,310
Star league?

384
00:36:39,447 --> 00:36:43,065
A refuge for weak worlds
not worthy to be our equals!

385
00:36:43,201 --> 00:36:45,408
That is for the rylans to decide,

386
00:36:45,537 --> 00:36:49,325
and not for a dangerous
and evil child such as yourself.

387
00:36:51,042 --> 00:36:56,207
And yet, it is this child
who caught your master spy.

388
00:37:25,577 --> 00:37:27,442
Hear me, rylans!

389
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:34,541
When the green moon of galan is
eclipsed, ko-Dan armada will invade,

390
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:40,505
and not even your mighty starfighters
will be able to save you.

391
00:37:40,633 --> 00:37:44,376
We shall see, xur. We shall see!

392
00:37:55,982 --> 00:38:01,147
Ha-ha! You still wanna go
and miss all the excitement?

393
00:38:06,451 --> 00:38:07,691
Little brat.

394
00:38:07,827 --> 00:38:10,159
I invent the game, find the kid,
drag him up there,

395
00:38:10,288 --> 00:38:14,201
and he doesn't wanna be a starfighter.
I give up!

396
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:54,738
'Control, do you copy our star
angle difference from parking angle?"

397
00:38:55,875 --> 00:39:00,494
'Delta beta two at six,
delta gamma three at five.'

398
00:39:06,094 --> 00:39:09,086
Emperor xur ordered me
to bring his scepter.

399
00:39:11,099 --> 00:39:12,680
Let him enter.

400
00:39:12,809 --> 00:39:15,266
"Target vector
remains on scope.'

401
00:39:29,951 --> 00:39:33,193
Just like your ko-Dan emperor's,
isn't it, commander kril?

402
00:39:33,329 --> 00:39:37,368
It takes more than a scepter
to rule, xur,

403
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:39,912
even on rylos.

404
00:39:42,338 --> 00:39:44,169
You're right, kiril.

405
00:39:46,009 --> 00:39:48,500
It does take more than a scepter.

406
00:39:57,270 --> 00:39:59,761
How long must we endure this fool?

407
00:40:01,733 --> 00:40:05,442
- We have a break in the frontier.
- Fire the meteor gun!

408
00:40:07,238 --> 00:40:11,151
My dear ko-Dan friends,
lest we forget,

409
00:40:11,284 --> 00:40:15,072
it was your own emperor who granted me
command of this armada.

410
00:40:15,204 --> 00:40:18,116
For only I hold the secret
to the frontier.

411
00:40:18,875 --> 00:40:21,491
Only I know the location
of the starfighter base.

412
00:40:21,628 --> 00:40:25,917
And therefore,
only I will give the order to fire!

413
00:40:29,636 --> 00:40:31,501
Forgive me, xur.

414
00:40:37,936 --> 00:40:40,348
You are forgiven, commander kiril.

415
00:40:43,942 --> 00:40:47,400
Meteor gunner... fire.

416
00:41:20,436 --> 00:41:21,846
Sergeant!

417
00:41:24,190 --> 00:41:28,559
I have an unidentified
incoming object in sector 31, sir.

418
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:34,231
They're headed for the base.

419
00:41:34,367 --> 00:41:38,610
Alert! We are under attack!
I repeat, we are under attack!

420
00:41:39,706 --> 00:41:42,163
Activate automatic repulser guns.

421
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:39,428
'Condition red! Condition red!

422
00:42:48,649 --> 00:42:50,389
At last, it is done!

423
00:42:51,903 --> 00:42:53,939
Soon the frontier will be down,

424
00:42:54,072 --> 00:42:56,529
and they will bow
to their new emperor!

425
00:42:57,241 --> 00:42:59,106
Or I will darken the sky
with their ashes.

426
