Commander, the xurian spy reports
that one starfighter has escaped.

427
00:43:03,915 --> 00:43:05,405
Escaped?

428
00:43:18,054 --> 00:43:19,510
Sure I can't give you a hand?

429
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:21,784
You've done quite enough
already. Thank you.

430
00:43:21,808 --> 00:43:23,264
Well, uh...

431
00:43:24,769 --> 00:43:28,682
It's only a few more miles from here.
I guess... I guess I can walk it.

432
00:43:28,815 --> 00:43:31,773
So long. Bye, centauri.

433
00:43:44,122 --> 00:43:45,987
Oh, Alex!

434
00:43:47,959 --> 00:43:49,369
Here!

435
00:43:53,422 --> 00:43:55,582
Hey, listen. I can't take a present
from you, centauri.

436
00:43:56,759 --> 00:43:59,671
He reduces me to poverty again
and he thinks I'm giving him a present.

437
00:43:59,804 --> 00:44:02,386
- What a world this is.
- What is it, then?

438
00:44:02,515 --> 00:44:04,380
It's a second chance, my boy!

439
00:44:04,517 --> 00:44:07,884
If you change your mind,
just tap the communo-crystals.

440
00:44:12,441 --> 00:44:14,807
