I told you, Alex.
Me and my... how did you put it?

452
00:45:20,134 --> 00:45:23,626
"Strange sexual urges"
aren't talking to you anymore.

453
00:46:04,553 --> 00:46:08,011
- Who's there!
- Shh! You're gonna wake up Louis.

454
00:46:16,691 --> 00:46:20,650
- Hey, you look like me!
- Of course I do. I'm the beta unit.

455
00:46:21,654 --> 00:46:24,020
What the hell's a beta unit?

456
00:46:24,156 --> 00:46:27,193
A beta unit is a simuloid,

457
00:46:27,326 --> 00:46:30,238
an exact duplicate of you,
only not as loud.

458
00:46:31,706 --> 00:46:33,913
- Huh?
- I was in the starcar, remember?

459
00:46:34,041 --> 00:46:37,909
We shook hands?
I became you, unfortunately.

460
00:46:39,714 --> 00:46:42,205
Let me get this straight.
You're a robot?

461
00:46:42,341 --> 00:46:44,297
I beg your pardon.

462
00:46:45,011 --> 00:46:48,674
I'm a state-of-the-art,
top-of-the-line beta unit,

463
00:46:48,806 --> 00:46:52,344
put here as a courtesy replacement
for while you're away.

464
00:46:52,476 --> 00:46:54,262
Lucky me.

465
00:46:54,395 --> 00:46:56,306
Wait a minute.
What are you doing back?

466
00:46:56,439 --> 00:46:57,975
Are you kidding? It's war up there!

467
00:46:58,107 --> 00:47:01,190
Oh. Save the whales
and not the universe, huh?

468
00:47:01,902 --> 00:47:03,733
Well, why don't you
go up there and fight?

469
00:47:03,863 --> 00:47:06,275
Simuloids can't fight.
We're not allowed.

470
00:47:06,407 --> 00:47:08,864
Well, tell them that you're me!
Pretend!

471
00:47:08,993 --> 00:47:11,109
Be quiet, Alex.

472
00:47:11,245 --> 00:47:13,156
Sorry, Louis.

473
00:47:13,956 --> 00:47:15,571
Thanks for the lift!

474
00:47:15,708 --> 00:47:18,370
Sure thing, buddy. See you around!

475
00:47:39,565 --> 00:47:41,430
'Greetings, starfighter.

476
00:47:41,567 --> 00:47:43,899
"You have been recruited
by the star league

477
00:47:44,028 --> 00:47:46,314
'to defend the frontier
against xur and..."

478
00:48:07,134 --> 00:48:08,590
And, hey, what did you do
to Maggie?

479
00:48:08,719 --> 00:48:10,129
Do to her?

480
00:48:10,262 --> 00:48:14,221
